										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The </span><a href="https://www.atfx.com.bz/en-ae/live-chart/gold-price" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span style="font-weight: 400;">price of gold</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> remains elevated after a recent rally above $2,500. </span></p>
<p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-40065" src="https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Gold-Daily-Chart.png" alt="Gold - Daily Chart" width="954" height="594" srcset="https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Gold-Daily-Chart.png 954w, https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Gold-Daily-Chart-300x187.png 300w, https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Gold-Daily-Chart-768x478.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 954px) 100vw, 954px" /></p>
